eligibility_criteria.description:
Minimum age: 10 Years
Maximum age: 60 Years
This trial does not accept healthy volunteers.
The subject has received investigational therapy within 30 days prior to first dose of study drug
Measurable or non-measurable disease per Response Evaluation Criteria in Solid Tumors (RECIST) version (v)1.1
Must be deemed medically fit for SBRT to the abdomen or thorax by the treating physician

groups.description: Patients use tongue depressors daily for 6 months. Patients with no improvement at 3 months cross over to Arm I.
groups.name: Arm II (tongue depressors)

groups.description: Patients receive pembrolizumab IV over 30 minutes on day 1. Patients also receive anti-FGFR3 monoclonal antibody B-701 IV over 30-90 minutes on days 1 and 8 of course 1, and day 1 of all subsequent courses. Courses repeat every 21 days in the absence of disease progression or unacceptable toxicity.

interventions.name: Drug, Food, Chemical or Biomedical Material

groups.name: Treatment (anti-FGFR3 monoclonal antibody, pembrolizumab)

outcome_measures.measure: Antitumor efficacy (complete and partial response rates)

outcome_measures.analysis_method: Will be estimated using Kaplan-Meier method.
outcome_measures.time_frame: Time from study entry or random assignment to disease progression in bone or soft-tissue, symptoms, or death, assessed up to 48 weeks

outcome_measures.analysis_method: Kaplan--Meier method will be used to analyze RFS time.
outcome_measures.time_frame: Time from date of response until the date of first objective documentation of disease-relapse, assessed up to 5 years

outcome_measures.analysis_method: A summary of adverse events will be tabulated at baseline and during treatment. Adverse event summaries will be organized by body system, frequency of occurrence, intensity (i.e., severity grade), and causality or attribution. Patients who experience an adverse event more than once will be counted only once. The occurrence with the maximum severity will be used to calculate intensity.
outcome_measures.measure: Incidence of long term toxicity to treatment using the NCI CTCAE v4.0
